    "title": "京东开放平台个人/个体店宠物生活和宠物健康品类招商激励政策（2026.2.01-2026.4.30）",
    "followRuleId": "1335877073803915264",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台宠物品类招商激励升级，符合条件商家可获得最长3个月平台运营支持服务费100%返还激励，激励以现金形式返还最高不超过50万，进一步降低新商家经营成本，助力新商家快速成长。具体内容如下：</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一、新商0扣点政策</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、参与商家（需同时满足以下条件）</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、2026年2月1日-2026年4月30日期间完成入驻的京东开放平台商家；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、店铺类型仅限个人店、个体店；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">指定类目</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一级类目：宠物生活、宠物健康；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二级类目：水族食品/用品、清洁用品、宠物服务、狗食品、宠物活体、猫狗玩具、猫狗出行、猫食品、洗护美容、小宠食品/用品、饮食居家用品、宠物营养保健、宠物医药器械；</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、激励政策</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">如商家满足要求，自动享受激励政策。当商家满足如下考核目标时，京东开放平台将于次月启动现金激励金额发放。具体内容如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、激励周期：完成入驻后的3个自然月（<strong>月度考核，例：2026年2月入驻的商家，第一个考核月份为2026年3月，次月开始发放现金激励</strong>）</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、激励规则：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）激励模式</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">：新商在指定时段内入驻，次月开始考核类目销售额。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（2）返还模式：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">按月度考核，并按月度整体达标档位发放。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（3）返还形式：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核达标后，次月以现金形式返还至京麦钱包。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（4）激励金额：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激励周期内激励类目产生实付扣点*激励比例，单月店铺最高激励金额为20000元</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、数据口径：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">销售额应为：为实收销售额，即考核期内店铺内该类目下单，且在2026年4月30日之前完成的订单产生的销售额【须剔除退货、未确认收货，取消订单、虚拟商品订单，刷单等风控订单、使用优惠券金额的订单等】，考核周期结束后，次月进行数据计算。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、其它说明</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）已享受平台特殊费率的订单所产生的GMV均计入本政策内进行达量考核，但不再给予本政策下返利。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（2）未产生扣点的商品销售额可计入激励考核，但不参与任何返点比例。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（3）此政策实施期间不与其他新商激励政策同享。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（4）激励周期内，若商家中途关店则激励终止。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、<strong>具体返利政策：（0.6%交易服务费另行单独收取，销售额单位：人民币元）</strong></span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 123.75pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"165\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.5pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">销售额要求</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 108.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"144\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">标准费率</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 141.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"188\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">返点比例</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"136\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">激励方式</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 123.75pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"165\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一档</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.5pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">单月销售额&ge;10000元</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 108.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"144\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2%/2.5%/5%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 141.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"188\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">返扣点的50%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"136\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">现金</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 123.75pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"165\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二档</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.5pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">单月销售额&ge;20000元</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 108.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"144\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2%/2.5%/5%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 141.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"188\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">返扣点的70%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"136\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">现金</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 123.75pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"165\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">三档</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.5pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">单月销售额&ge;30000元</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 108.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"144\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2%/2.5%/5%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 141.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"188\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">返扣点的100%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"136\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">现金</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">返激励公式示例：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2026</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年2月15日完成店铺入驻的商家，激励周期为2026年3月1日~2026年5月31日，若商家在某个激励期间（月度）全店GMV为25000元，则成功完成二档的目标（二档：考核周期内单月销售额&ge;20000元），激励金额 = 累计全店销售额对应档位金额（25000元）* 类目运营支持服务费费率*激励比例（70%）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">注：店铺ID归属于京喜事业部下，具体店铺归属请咨询各店铺/类目运营，政策考核期内数据、激励金额最终以京东确认的数据为准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、政策发布期间如有策略调整，可能会对激励、返还政策做出调整、中止或终止，调整政策是否追溯适用以京东公告为准。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">三、违约责任</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">若商家在激励周期内发生以下任一情形，则京东开放平台有权取消商家因此获得的全部激励且不承担任何责任；如激励已发放，则京东开放平台有权自任意一笔待与商家结算的款项中或商家已缴纳的保证金中直接扣除激励金，不足抵扣的，京东开放平台有权保留继续追偿的权利：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家及其关联方采取不正当手段（如刷单、套券、重复开店套利等）获取激励的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家存在恶意竞争、影响消费者权益、影响京东平台声誉等违反市场公平竞争原则、诚实信用原则、公序良俗的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、其余违反《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反《京东开放平台招商资质标准细则》的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反其他京东平台规则的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、若激励导致平台大额亏损，平台会即时停止激励活动。</span></p>",
